Type: Package
Package: distiller
Title: Distill EPHT Data Down To XML
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Alexander", "Senetcky", , "asenetcky@gmail.com.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0009-3730-5397"))
Description: EPHT data submission has alot documentation, much of it
    is buried and out of date, making it difficult for new users to
    decipher the exact specifications of the data submissions' XML.
    `distiller` aims to make it easier to created the desired XML.
